This paper is about a framework for sequence-to-sequence modeling, which is a common task in natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which focuses on NLP. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning, which is a common topic in cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions the support for distributed training, which is a common topic in cs.CV (Computer Vision).
